USA: Ivory Coast gets $10 mln in PL480 to buy rice.Ivory Coast gets $10 mln in PL480 to buy rice.An authorization to buy $10 million worth of U.S. rice under PL480 was issued to Cote D'Ivoire, the U.S. Agriculture Department said Tuesday.USDA said the authorization provides for the purchase of about 22,000 tonnes of long, medium or short-grain milled rice or brown rice for processing.The contracting period is August 26 through September 30 and the delivery period is August 26 through December 31.